---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const isEn = true;
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Dowithsudo" isEn={isEn}>
  <main class="container-custom py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert lg:prose-xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-accent">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-primary-foreground/70 mb-6">Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US')}</p>

      <section class="space-y-8 text-primary-foreground/80">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using Dowithsudo services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions. If you do not agree, please refrain from using our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground">2. Scope of Services</h2>
          <p>Dowithsudo provides professional IT support including but not limited to technical consulting, server management, and software installation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Providing accurate information regarding technical issues.</li>
            <li>Ensuring regular data backups before any work begins.</li>
            <li>Providing necessary access (physical or remote) to complete tasks.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground">4. Payment</h2>
          <p>Payments must be made according to the issued invoice. We reserve the right to suspend services in case of late payments.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Dowithsudo is not responsible for data loss caused by hardware failure or factors beyond our control. Users are fully responsible for their own data security.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>